<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Cab Booking</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="path/to/your/font-awesome/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #343a40;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-section {
            background-image: url('path/to/your/hero-image.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            color: black;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #0056b3;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .team-member {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

            .team-member img {
                max-width: 35%;
                border-radius: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                border: 5px solid #ffffff;
                box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
            }

                .team-member img:hover {
                    transform: scale(1.1);
                }

        .contact-form {
            text-align: center;
        }

            .contact-form input,
            .contact-form textarea {
                width: 100%;
                padding: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 15px;
                border: 1px solid #ccc;
                border-radius: 5px;
            }

            .contact-form button {
                background-color: #0056b3;
                color: #ffffff;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                border: none;
                border-radius: 5px;
                cursor: pointer;
                transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            }

                .contact-form button:hover {
                    background-color: #003366;
                }

        /* Add more styles and animations as needed */
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1 class="animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">About Us</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="hero-section">
        <h2 class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">Experience the Future of Cab Booking</h2>
        <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">We have a fine quality of cars that are available 24*7 at your service.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <section>
            <h2 class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">We have a mission to make our vision of providing a comfortable travel experience in the most cost-effective manner possible. Over the coming years, we would like to expand our venture to other states and will try to bring the feeling of comfort in the lives of our customers.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">Our Team</h2>

            <div class="team-member animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
                <img src="~/css/IMG_20230918_190652_093 (1).jpg" alt="Team Member 1">
                <h3>Vivek Kumar</h3>
                <p>CEO</p>
            </div>
            <br />
            <br />
            

            <!-- Add more team members as needed -->
        </section>

       @*  <section class="contact-form">
            <h2 class="animate__animated animate__fadeIn">Contact Us</h2>
